1948;;A Date with a Dream;;British;;Dicky Leeman;;Terry-Thomas, Jeannie Carson;;musical/comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Date_with_a_Dream;;When an Army concert party is disbanded after the war, they plan to meet up in a years time for a reunion. When they do they discover that all the various members aren't coping too well with civilian life. Jean, a singer who is staying in the same house as two of the ex-concert party members, suggests that the various members get back together to perform.[3]